readme.text:
thirdweb Wallet SDK

Unified web3 Wallet library to integrate any wallet into your applications.


### A unified interface for ANY wallet

### Supported wallets

#### Browser wallets

- Metamask
- Coinbase Wallet
- Wallet Connect v1 and v2
- Smart Wallet (ERC-4337)
- Local Wallet
- Paper Wallet
- Magic.link
- Ethers

#### Backend Wallets

- Private key
- AWS KMs
- AWS Secret Manager

#### Documentation

https://portal.thirdweb.com/wallet
